highlights.text: Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #37.
“ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 950 days straight.
“ไปได้ดี (So Long)” by WANYAi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 78 spots at #112.
“Rich Man” by aespa is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #3.
